<p><span style="font-size: 24px;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 1px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 29.9999px; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-shadow: none; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">日常生活中，我们总能在班里听到这样的话：“xxx，你也太卷了吧，又在学习”，亦或是“哎呀，太累，我准备躺平了”。“躺”和“卷”近来成为了学生们的口头禅，为了引导学生们正确理解“躺”和“卷”，树立正确的价值观，12月7日晚19：00，经济管理学院在A10-306教室开展以“卷躺达人手册”为主题的班会，本次班会由辅导员</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 1px; text-align: justify; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2.28571em; caret-color: red; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">江雅婷老师主持召开，并邀请了其他学院的老师来观摩。</span></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px; text-align: justify; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2.28571em; caret-color: red; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240113/1705117707290038551.jpg" title="1705117707290038551.jpg" alt="d35e34891cecab530d7ebee6a6279d97.jpg" width="832" height="372" style="width: 832px; height: 372px;"/></span></p>